OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FITV News International Editor Emma
OL,7,FMurphy reports from Tehran as Trump
OL,8,Fannounced a two-week ceasefire
OL,10,FAfter 39 days of this war, a ceasefire
OL,11,Fis now in place. Here in Tehran, the
OL,12,Fdawn does not echo to the sound of
OL,13,Fexplosions.
OL,15,FOn paper, at least, or on social
OL,16,Fmedia, diplomacy's modern-day
OL,17,Fequivalent, there is an agreed 14-day
OL,18,Fpause.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
