OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775639132
OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FThe deal came in the early hours,
OL,7,Fafter maximalist threats, escalating
OL,8,Frhetoric, ferocious attacks and
OL,9,Ffrantic global diplomacy.
OL,11,FFor it to last, the serious hard work
OL,12,Fof finding a sustainable and enduring
OL,13,Fsolution must now begin. War is the
OL,14,Feasier part; peace will be the
OL,15,Fchallenge.
OL,17,FEvery player will claim their victory,
OL,18,Fbut this war has exposed strengths and
OL,19,Fweaknesses of great hegemons and this
OL,20,Fpause will expose divisions which will
OL,21,Fbe hard to bridge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
