CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775639132
OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FNations' sense of dominance, power and
OL,7,Fsafety has been shaken along with the
OL,8,Fglobal economy. The cost will be
OL,9,Fenduring and felt near and far.
OL,11,FAnd what has really been achieved
OL,12,Fapart from chaos? The myriad of ever-
OL,13,Fchanging war objectives laid out by
OL,14,Fthe United States may have sought to
OL,15,Fobscure success and failure, but the
OL,16,Freality on the ground puts the
OL,17,Fjeopardy of this war into clear focus.
OL,19,FNone of the fundamental issues have
OL,20,Fbeen resolved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
