OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775639132
OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FThis is certainly not the
OL,7,F"unconditional surrender" US President
OL,8,FDonald Trump so confidently predicted.
OL,10,FThe Islamic Republic remains, many of
OL,11,Fits leaders, from the late Ayotollah
OL,12,Fdown, have been killed, but it is
OL,13,Fstill very much in power in this
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FIts missile stock is diminished, but
OL,17,Fnot to the level that has been claimed
OL,18,Ffor weeks. Its nuclear stockpile
OL,19,Fremains, including the highly enriched
OL,20,Furanium over which two wars have now
OL,21,Fbeen fought.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775639132
OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FAnd the surviving leaders of the
OL,7,FIslamic Republic have proved a
OL,8,Fresilience that was miscalculated from
OL,9,Fthe get-go.
OL,11,FDespite more than 13,000 strikes on
OL,12,Ftheir territory, they proved their
OL,13,Fpower in the Strait of Hormuz could
OL,14,Falmost cripple the world economy.
OL,16,FThat power was fundamentally
OL,17,Fmiscalculated by those who launched
OL,18,Fthis war, and it leaves in Iran's
OL,19,Fhands a power which was not used
OL,20,Fbefore this war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
