OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FThere will be some here who do not
OL,7,Fwelcome this pause and will not trust
OL,8,Fit. Another of President Trump's
OL,9,Fpromises was to deliver help to
OL,10,Fprotestors. That help has not
OL,11,Fdelivered the results they had sought.
OL,13,FEvery one of those points will be seen
OL,14,Fby the Iranian government as a
OL,15,Fhumiliation to the West and a
OL,16,Fvalidation of their resilience under
OL,17,Fextreme pressure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
