OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FAs for Trump, his threat, in place for
OL,7,Fmore than ten hours, that "a whole
OL,8,Fcivilization will die tonight, never
OL,9,Fto be brought back again" will not be
OL,10,Fforgotten by friend or foe.
OL,12,FIt will be claimed as an artful way of
OL,13,Fbringing the tactics of the boardroom
OL,14,Finto geopolitics, but the threat to
OL,15,Fthe lives of millions is an abuse of
OL,16,Fpower not easily dismissed as bluster.
OL,18,FAnd what of his allies, those Gulf
OL,19,Fstates, who thought the warm arm of
OL,20,FAmerican association offered them a
OL,21,Fprotection?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
