OL,3,CInside Iran: Finally there's a pause -
OL,4,Cbut now the really hard work must begin
OL,6,FHow quickly the missiles and drones
OL,7,Ftore through that costly illusion.
OL,9,FFor 20 years, Western leaders have
OL,10,Fsought to control the Islamic Republic
OL,11,Fthrough negotiation.
OL,13,FTwice now, Trump has sought to break
OL,14,Fthem through war.
OL,16,FOver the next two weeks, a solution
OL,17,Fwill need to be found to bridge the
OL,18,Fvast gaps between East and West, or
OL,19,Fthis war will simply be the latest,
OL,20,Fnot the last.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
